Like you have ten children together, tie their eyes

00:19:38.151 --> 00:19:42.791
ask them about somebody: "What is wrong with this person?"

00:19:51.985 --> 00:19:56.107
Now, all your centers are in your hand reflected,

00:19:56.308 --> 00:20:01.782
sympathetic, five, six, seven centers.

