But when you don't forgive, then you play into wrong hands.

00:34:18.642 --> 00:34:22.833
Those who have troubled you and have tortured you are happy,

00:34:23.033 --> 00:34:27.767
and you are torturing yourself on their behalf.

00:34:35.215 --> 00:34:42.997
But also the center of optical chiasma is like that in the Agnya Chakra.

00:34:49.304 --> 00:34:54.760
