00:40:18.557 --> 00:40:23.373
Then we take our right hand in the lower portion of abdomen

00:40:23.573 --> 00:40:27.276
on left hand side,

00:40:31.573 --> 00:40:39.682
which is the center of pure knowledge of Divine Laws.

00:40:44.513 --> 00:40:50.614
Then we raise again our right hand in the upper portion of abdomen.

00:40:54.786 --> 00:40:58.613
Then on our heart.

00:40:59.168 --> 00:41:02.703
Then in the corner of our neck and our shoulder

00:41:02.903 --> 00:41:06.536
and turn our head to right.

00:41:12.993 --> 00:41:17.254
I've already told you about this center that when you feel guilty,

00:41:17.454 --> 00:41:21.259
it goes out of order.

00:41:26.485 --> 00:41:32.363
Now we take our right hand and put it across our forehead

00:41:32.563 --> 00:41:36.407
and put down our head.

00:41:40.704 --> 00:41:48.555
This is the center to forgive everyone in general.

00:41:53.375 --> 00:41:58.902
Now we take back our right hand on the back side of our head

00:41:59.102 --> 00:42:03.797
and push back our head as far as possible.

00:42:10.828 --> 00:42:15.847
This is the center where without feeling guilty,

00:42:16.047 --> 00:42:20.050
without counting your mistakes, just for your satisfaction,

00:42:20.250 --> 00:42:25.125
you have to ask forgiveness from the Divine Power.

00:42:33.812 --> 00:42:36.210
Now the last center, you have to

00:42:36.411 --> 00:42:41.060
stretch your palm fully.

00:42:45.632 --> 00:42:50.671
And put the center of your palm on top of fontanel bone area

00:42:50.872 --> 00:42:55.601
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

00:43:02.962 --> 00:43:06.493
Now please bend your head.

00:43:08.079 --> 00:43:11.076
Very important is to push back your fingers,

00:43:11.276 --> 00:43:15.244
so that there is a good pression on your scalp.

00:43:25.553 --> 00:43:35.037
Please now move your scalp clockwise seven times slowly.

00:43:44.006 --> 00:43:47.928
Please put down your hands.

00:43:49.904 --> 00:43:52.211
That is all we have to do now.

00:43:52.412 --> 00:43:54.634
We have to now close our eyes

00:43:54.834 --> 00:43:59.381
and please don't open them till I tell you.

00:44:05.968 --> 00:44:09.960
You can take out your glasses.

00:44:14.706 --> 00:44:18.757
Now, again, please put both feet apart from each other,

00:44:18.957 --> 00:44:23.707
put left hand like this and the right hand on the heart.

00:44:30.602 --> 00:44:34.829
And now please close your eyes.

00:44:37.532 --> 00:44:41.386
Here resides the Spirit,

00:44:41.586 --> 00:44:46.474
so you have to ask Me a very fundamental question about yourself.

00:44:46.674 --> 00:44:51.620
You may call Me Mother or you may call Me Shri Mataji.

00:45:01.853 --> 00:45:08.017
Please ask Me three time in your heart: "Mother, am I the Spirit?"

00:45:20.351 --> 00:45:24.823
I already told you that if you are the Spirit,

00:45:25.023 --> 00:45:29.187
you become your own master.

00:45:35.210 --> 00:45:37.612
So now, please take your right hand

00:45:37.812 --> 00:45:41.960
in the upper portion of your abdomen on the left hand side.

00:45:47.610 --> 00:45:51.508
You are working only on the left hand side.

00:45:53.406 --> 00:46:02.027
Here again you have to ask a fundamental question three times:

00:46:02.227 --> 00:46:06.711
"Mother, am I my own master?"

00:46:15.152 --> 00:46:21.551
Now, I have already told you that I respect your freedom

00:46:21.751 --> 00:46:29.043
and I cannot force the pure knowledge of Divine on you,

00:46:29.243 --> 00:46:32.982
you have to ask for it.

00:46:41.121 --> 00:46:43.148
So now you have to take your right hand

00:46:43.348 --> 00:46:45.748
in the lower portion of your abdomen

00:46:45.949 --> 00:46:50.133
on the left hand side and press it and here

00:46:50.333 --> 00:46:52.774
you have to ask six times,

00:46:52.974 --> 00:46:57.368
because this center has got six petals.

00:46:57.568 --> 00:47:05.833
Please say six time: "Mother, please give me pure knowledge."

00:47:30.197 --> 00:47:35.872
As soon as you ask for pure knowledge,

00:47:36.072 --> 00:47:39.281
your Kundalini starts rising.

00:47:39.481 --> 00:47:49.300
So now you have to enrich your higher centers

00:47:49.500 --> 00:47:54.508
with your full self-confidence.

00:48:10.590 --> 00:48:13.538
So now raise your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen

00:48:13.738 --> 00:48:18.098
on the left hand side and press it.

00:48:22.483 --> 00:48:28.627
Here with full confidence, you have to say ten times:

00:48:28.827 --> 00:48:33.506
"Mother, I am my own master."

00:48:56.699 --> 00:49:01.859
I have already told you the fundamental truth about you

00:49:02.059 --> 00:49:07.726
that you are not this body, this mind, this ego, these conditionings,

00:49:07.926 --> 00:49:12.192
but you are the pure Spirit.

00:49:22.398 --> 00:49:28.112
So now, please raise your right hand on top of your heart

00:49:28.312 --> 00:49:34.706
and here you have to say with full confidence twelve times:

00:49:34.906 --> 00:49:40.476
"Mother, I am the pure Spirit."

00:50:01.893 --> 00:50:09.190
This All Pervading Power of Divine Love is the ocean of knowledge.

00:50:14.893 --> 00:50:23.940
It is the ocean of compassion and ocean of bliss.

00:50:27.659 --> 00:50:32.498
It is the ocean of miracles.

00:50:32.698 --> 00:50:37.604
But above all, It is the ocean of forgiveness.

00:50:40.339 --> 00:50:43.826
And all your mistakes can be easily dissolve

00:50:44.026 --> 00:50:48.425
by this ocean of forgiveness.

00:50:52.193 --> 00:50:55.798
So please forgive yourself and raise your right hand

00:50:55.998 --> 00:50:58.368
in the corner of your neck and your shoulder

00:50:58.568 --> 00:51:02.373
and turn your head to right.

00:51:13.863 --> 00:51:18.042
Please turn it to right.

00:51:20.214 --> 00:51:25.678
Now here you have to say with full self-confidence:

00:51:25.878 --> 00:51:31.300
"Mother, I am not guilty at all."

00:51:47.834 --> 00:51:51.087
I've already told you that

00:51:51.287 --> 00:51:57.146
logically whether you forgive or don't forgive, you don't do anything.

00:52:03.106 --> 00:52:09.817
But if you don't forgive, the you play into wrong hands all your life.

00:52:13.345 --> 00:52:17.004
And at this juncture, if you don't forgive,

00:52:17.204 --> 00:52:19.567
your Agnya Chakra won't open

00:52:19.767 --> 00:52:25.603
and the Kundalini will not be able to penetrate through it.

00:52:32.574 --> 00:52:37.171
So you have already tortured yourself all your life and now

00:52:37.371 --> 00:52:41.957
at this great moment, you miss your Self Realization.

00:52:49.781 --> 00:52:52.831
So now say in your heart,

00:52:53.031 --> 00:52:55.917
not how many times, but from your heart:

00:52:56.117 --> 00:53:03.094
"Mother, I forgive everyone in general." Don't think about them.

00:53:23.807 --> 00:53:27.248
Now you have to take your hand on the back side of your head

00:53:27.448 --> 00:53:30.920
and push back your head as far as possible.

00:53:31.120 --> 00:53:35.670
Here, without feeling guilty, without counting your mistakes,

00:53:35.870 --> 00:53:42.315
just for your satisfaction, you have to say,

00:53:57.101 --> 00:54:01.287
say from your heart, not how many times:

00:54:05.553 --> 00:54:09.345
"Oh Divine Power, if I have done any mistakes,

00:54:09.545 --> 00:54:14.194
knowingly or unknowingly, please forgive me."

00:54:33.125 --> 00:54:37.768
Now, the last center, is very important,

00:54:37.968 --> 00:54:42.226
we have to stretch our palm fully.

00:54:48.317 --> 00:54:52.430
And now we have to put our center of our palm

00:54:52.630 --> 00:54:56.973
on top of fontanel bone area.

00:55:02.925 --> 00:55:07.457
Now stretch back your fingers, that's important.

00:55:10.582 --> 00:55:14.527
And please put down your head as far as possible.

00:55:20.036 --> 00:55:32.561
Here I again cannot cross over your freedom.

00:55:37.806 --> 00:55:48.312
Again you have to ask Me to give you Self Realization.

00:55:53.727 --> 00:55:57.808
So now move your scalp slowly

00:55:58.009 --> 00:56:00.979
clockwise seven times saying:

00:56:01.180 --> 00:56:06.883
"Mother, please give me Self Realization", seven times.

00:57:26.478 --> 00:57:30.244
Please take down your hands.

00:57:32.525 --> 00:57:36.883
And open your eyes, please.

00:57:38.391 --> 00:57:42.047
Please put both the hands towards Me like this.

00:57:49.213 --> 00:57:53.025
Like this, not like that.

00:57:54.197 --> 00:57:58.572
And watch Me without thinking.

00:58:00.230 --> 00:58:05.176
Now bend your head and see with your left hand

00:58:05.377 --> 00:58:10.739
if there's a cool, warm or a hot breeze like wave

00:58:10.939 --> 00:58:14.439
coming out of your own head.

00:58:24.877 --> 00:58:29.830
Put your hand on top of your head, but away from it.

00:58:34.110 --> 00:58:38.009
Some people get it too far.

00:58:41.727 --> 00:58:45.532
Now please put the left hand towards Me like this.

00:58:48.173 --> 00:58:50.863
And bend your head and now see with your right hand

00:58:51.063 --> 00:58:55.895
if there's a cool, warm or a hot breeze like wave

00:58:56.095 --> 00:58:59.860
coming out of your fontanel bone area.

00:59:09.023 --> 00:59:12.697
If it is warm or hot, it means you are not forgiving,

00:59:12.898 --> 00:59:17.346
so please forgive.

00:59:22.190 --> 00:59:27.018
I cannot forgive for you, you have to forgive yourself.

00:59:32.190 --> 00:59:34.777
Now, please put right hand.

00:59:34.978 --> 00:59:39.048
Bend your heads, bend your heads.

00:59:42.767 --> 00:59:49.012
And see with your left hand, if there's a cool breeze like waves

00:59:49.212 --> 00:59:55.509
or hot or warm coming out of your fontanel bone area.

01:00:03.497 --> 01:00:06.266
Now, please do it.

01:00:06.466 --> 01:00:10.458
Put both the hands towards the sky.

01:00:13.763 --> 01:00:17.536
And push back your head.

01:00:19.982 --> 01:00:26.396
Now, ask anyone of these three questions three times.

01:00:32.579 --> 01:00:40.754
"Mother, is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?"

01:00:40.954 --> 01:00:49.102
Or "Mother, is this the All Pervading Power of Love, Divine Love?"

01:00:54.643 --> 01:00:59.229
Or "Is it Brahma Chaitanya."

01:00:59.503 --> 01:01:03.792
Anyone of these questions, you can ask three times.

01:01:09.732 --> 01:01:13.575
Now take down your hands.

01:01:20.847 --> 01:01:23.901
Put your hands like this.

01:01:28.276 --> 01:01:32.089
You can feel your silence within yourself.

01:01:36.190 --> 01:01:42.975
Now, all those who have felt cool breeze on their fingertips,

01:01:43.175 --> 01:01:46.615
or hot or warm breeze on their fingertips,

01:01:46.815 --> 01:01:54.232
or the same on their hands or out of their fontanel bone area,

01:01:54.432 --> 01:01:58.893
please raise both your hands.

01:02:10.699 --> 01:02:14.561
Please raise both.

01:02:14.761 --> 01:02:18.839
That is Brasilia. May God Bless you.

01:02:20.472 --> 01:02:25.808
I bow to you all. You all have started your saintly life.

01:02:31.363 --> 01:02:35.379
Every where, all of you have got it.

01:02:37.637 --> 01:02:41.765
May God bless you all.

01:02:41.965 --> 01:02:48.918
There is to be - it is to be understood that you have gone beyond your mind.

01:02:53.490 --> 01:02:57.740
So don't argue and don't doubt.

01:03:01.052 --> 01:03:05.313
We have here a very good center for you,

01:03:05.513 --> 01:03:10.560
where you must learn how to make this connection perfect.

01:03:18.388 --> 01:03:26.271
All the knowledge about your subtle system, everything you will know.

01:03:32.456 --> 01:03:37.838
But one should know that you can only grow in collectivity.

01:03:42.540 --> 01:03:48.501
Supposing one nail is cut out of My body, it will never grow.

01:03:52.987 --> 01:03:59.115
So you have to be humble about it and you should, all of you,

01:03:59.315 --> 01:04:02.940
master this art.

01:04:08.577 --> 01:04:14.873
You will have the powers to raise the Kundalini of others and awaken them.

01:04:19.338 --> 01:04:23.448
You can cure people, you can do so many things.

01:04:26.760 --> 01:04:30.549
And for all this, you don't have to pay at all.

01:04:34.221 --> 01:04:36.681
You don't have to be also obliged,

01:04:36.882 --> 01:04:41.182
because it is your own power it has worked it.

01:04:45.855 --> 01:04:50.121
It is your honest seeking it has worked out.

01:04:54.707 --> 01:04:57.717
I will definitely come next year here again for a longer period.

01:04:57.918 --> 01:05:01.864
por um período mais longo.

01:05:05.299 --> 01:05:09.740
I would love you all to grow into your wisdom

01:05:09.940 --> 01:05:14.283
like a great tree of spirituality.

01:05:20.971 --> 01:05:24.596
May God Bless you all.
